.TH "pci_epc_set_bar" 9 "pci_epc_set_bar" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
pci_epc_set_bar \- configure BAR in order for host to assign PCI addr space
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" pci_epc_set_bar
.BI "(struct pci_epc *epc "  ","
.BI "u8 func_no "  ","
.BI "struct pci_epf_bar *epf_bar "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "epc" 12
the EPC device on which BAR has to be configured
.IP "func_no" 12
the endpoint function number in the EPC device
.IP "epf_bar" 12
the struct epf_bar that contains the BAR information
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Invoke to configure the BAR of the endpoint device.
